metadata.name: The FIRE of your Gaze
metadata.description:
The path of destruction and love. Truth is important, the path to the
truth also has obstacles, getting lost is normal; It is difficult to
imagine life without it being by your side but I am sure of something,
the light is near. The fire of your soul motivates you, it directs you
to power, balance, passion and goodness; there will also be
disappointment, anger, rage, sadness, repentance... a lot of
repentance but acceptance of change, in life there are changes that
one does not expect, there will be fear of not doing the right thing,
of not repeating what was lived in Every morning at the same time with
that beautiful smile that fills your soul with energy and by your side
you have the love of your life that will never fail you with a cup of
coffee every morning. Att: the fire of your gaze.
